reviewText: Gallagher has gotten older and officially no longer cares, but it's still hilarious! :)
It was a great gift! I had never heard of Gallagher before, but the person who received the gift enjoyed it! Thanks!

I loved Gallagher back in the day but don't get these shows.  Worst shows I've ever seen.
He has gotten so bitter and it really shows.  Crude & Rude.

I've followed Gallagher for many years and even saw him perform in person. He's funny because he speaks the truth about so many subjects and makes them funny! Love him after all theses years..devoted fan here!
This was very disappointing.  I am an old fan of Gallagher, but this video does not live up to his norm.

The show was one of the most unorganized, which I expect a little from since it's live but not quite this extreme. There were lines being forgotten and goofy computer animated scenes in between acts. Gallagher usually does something along these lines in his shows, but the material wasn't there to counteract it. It's definitely worth watching, but it's not going on the shelf with his Sledge-O-Matic collection.
